records.addlTxt: Voluntary appearance on November 10, 2022 at 01:00 pm.

2:31 PM Defendant Nathanial Zacharia Johnson not in court.  Attorney Stephanie E Thomas-Schmidt in court for Nathanial Zacharia Johnson.  Attorney Aaron B Marcoux in court for State of Wisconsin. Court calls case and appearances. No appearance by defendant. Status from Atty Thomas-Schmidt re: whereabouts of the defendant. State requests a warrant-Argument from Atty Thomas-Schmidt-requesting the warrant be stayed. Court speaks to JA re: Court will authorize warrant, but stayed until 11/7 @ 430.

1:32 PM Defendant Nathanial Zacharia Johnson in court.  Attorney Alysja Otten appeared specially by video for Nathanial Zacharia Johnson.  Attorney Aaron B Marcoux in court for State of Wisconsin. Court calls case and appearances. Parties are ready to proceed. State calls Deputy Drew Knoop to the stand. Clerk swears in. State begins questioning. State offers exhibit 1-Lab Test Results.  Court finds the witness identifies the defendant. Court receives exhibit 1. Nothing further. Cross from Atty Otten. Nothing further. Court questions the witness. Redirect from the State. State offers exhibit 2 and exhibit 3-No objections-received.  Nothing further. Witness excused. Argument from the State. Argument from Atty Otten. Court finds probable cause.
Arraignment scheduled for October 31, 2022 at 02:30 pm.

Absolute sobriety. 
Not to drive w/out a valid DL.
